usage() {
  cat <<'EOF'
Usage:
  kubeton <command>

Commands:
  install              Install or upgrade operator only (Helm upgrade --install with operator-values.yaml).
  bootstrap-baremetal  Prepare key prerequisites: Longhorn+Vault on bare-metal, local StorageClass+Vault on k3d.
  start                Start TON fleet.
  prometheus start     Create/update Prometheus pod(s) for TonNode exporter targets and start local background port-forward.
  prometheus stop      Stop/drop kubeton-managed Prometheus resources and local background port-forward(s).
  grafana start        Create/update Grafana, provision kubeton Prometheus datasource(s) and starter dashboard(s), and start local background port-forward.
  grafana stop         Stop/drop kubeton-managed Grafana resources and local background port-forward(s).
  victoria-metrics install    Install VictoriaMetrics operator + VMSingle/VMAgent/VMAuth stack, configure TonNode scraping, and start local background port-forward.
  victoria-metrics uninstall  Remove kubeton-managed VictoriaMetrics stack resources and local background port-forward(s).
  add                  Add one fresh TON replica to the existing TON StatefulSet (resets leftover target-ordinal PVCs if present).
  del                  Delete the tail TON pod replica (highest ordinal) with its PVC/PV/Longhorn volume.
  recreate             Recreate one TON pod data volumes and restore its encrypted key bundle: kubeton recreate <pod-name|namespace/pod-name> <backup-dir>.
  backup-keys          Trigger manual encrypted backup, export key bundles, restore TON replicas.
  restore-keys         Restore encrypted key bundles from backup dir, then restart TON replicas.
  stop                 Stop TON fleet (sets TonNode replicas to 0; keeps operator/TonNode/StatefulSet/PVC). Backup is skipped by default; set SKIP_STOP_KEY_BACKUP=false to run stop-time backup.
  drop                 Stop TON fleet + delete TonNode resources + delete TON PVCs (with confirmation).
  uninstall            Stop/drop TON fleet + remove kubeton-managed observability stacks + uninstall operator, Longhorn, and Vault (with confirmation; keeps TonNode CRD).
  purge                Full destructive cleanup: uninstall (including kubeton-managed observability stacks) + delete TonNode CRD (separate to avoid accidental cluster-wide CRD removal).
  verify               Verify operator and TON resources (deploy, pods with node/server, tonnodes, sts, pvc).
  status               Run wallet/adnl/sync/db checks in each TON pod; print node/pod/wallet/adnl/sync/cell db/archive db.
  exec <cmd>           Run a command in each TON pod and print table with node/pod/exit code.

Environment overrides:
  RELEASE_NAME, OP_NAMESPACE, CHART_DIR, OP_VALUES_FILE, TON_VALUES_FILE, TON_POD_LABEL
  TON_NAMESPACE
